Ink pen (Testcases)
-Check the pen is filled with ink first
-Check the ink flow through the nib smoothly
-Check the pen by writing in a paper to see the flow of ink (because the ink should not overflow)
-Check you can hold the pen comfortably
-Check the pen should not make any sound while writing
-Check the pen does not have any sharp edges
-check there is no leakage of ink in the pen by holding it by different positions.
-check the pen is having quality nib because it may break while writing
-check after writing the ink is dried quickly because it may spread to hands
